data.description: Country living just outside the city! Bring your horses, bring your chickens, bring everyone to this 6 bedroom home located on 4+ acres just outside the city. This home has undergone quite the transformation... Foundation repaired last year, freshly painted inside and out, updated baths, updated utility room, garage and breezeway professionally converted, updated electrical panel, tankless water heater, 3 HVAC units installed in 2016 with all new ductwork, 20x20 carport with a 10x20 storage area, 20x20 Red Winslow storage building, new carpet installed last month, new gutters in 2020, and a chicken coop with a large run is already in place, etc... This property is priced to move quickly!
